man from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\">House Manderly</a> and the daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Theomore_Manderly\" title=\"Theomore Manderly\">Theomore Manderly</a>. She had at least three brothers and a sister.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jessamyn_Manderly&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> visited <a href=\"/index.php/White_Harbor\" title=\"White Harbor\">White Harbor</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_58_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">58&#160;AC</a> during a <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_progress\" title=\"Royal progress\">royal progress</a>, Jessamyn acted as Alysanne's <a href=\"/index.php/Cupbearer\" title=\"Cupbearer\">cupbearer</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-excerpt_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-excerpt-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jessamyn_Manderly&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rows